        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加innerFirst到2nd的连接，Second内部也放好了Education_GradeSync。现在处理Third？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "innerFirst",
        "2nd",
        "Second",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Third内部有Education_StudentDB，从它引出3rd状态，然后3rd要连回Education_ContentCDN，形成一个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Third",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "3rd",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，之前Education_ContentCDN已经在innerFirst里面作为1st1st的入口了。现在3rd又连回Education_ContentCDN，这是同一个节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
